ARTICLE.TITLE: Census Bureau offering on hand assistance at the Amarillo Community Market
ARTICLE.TEXT: Answers can only be used to produce statistics and the Census does not share information with immigration or law enforcement agencies or allow it to be used to do determine eligibility for government benefits.

METADATA.description: Census Bureau is offering questionnaire assistance at the Amarillo Community Market on Saturday, August 15th from 9:00 am to 12:00 pm.
